label: A_cF32_227_e-001
title: T-Carbon Structure
comments:
This was predicted by (Sheng, 2011) and found experimentally by (Xu, 2020) and others. 
 The ICSD entry is from (Kang, 2020), who gave the atomic positions in terms of setting 1 of space group $Fd\overline{3}m$ \#227.  We used FINDSYM to change this to the standard setting 2.
